high_descs: Turn around and go to the sidetable.
Take the pencil from the side table of the bedroom.
Turn around and go near the mug.
Put the pencil in the mug on the table.
Take the mug along with pencil from the table.
Turn around and go near the shelf.
Put the mug with pencil on the shelf.
anns.task_desc: Placed the Mug along with Pencil on the Shelf.

high_descs: Turn left and walk into the bedroom with a small sidetable.
Pick up the white pencil from the side table.
Turn right and walk up to the wooden mug.
Put the pencil into the dark mug on the desk.
Pick up the mug with the pencil in it.
Turn right and approach the light colored shelf.
Put the mug with the pencil down on the shelf.
anns.task_desc: Put the pencil and mug on the shelf.

high_descs: Turn left. Go ahead. Cross to the left. Turn right. Enter the room. Turn right and then left, you are in front of the sidetable.
Grab the pencil.
Turn around, move. Turn left. When you exit, turn left again and then right to the far left of the mug.
Place the pencil in the mug.
Grab the mug and the pen.
Turn right and approach the shelf.
Place the mug and pen below the shelf.
anns.task_desc: Find a pencil and a mug. Bring them to the shelf.
